Actions.Text: REFERRED TO HOUSING, CONSTRUCTION AND COMMUNITY DEVELOPMENT

Title: Relates to the removal of unauthorized persons from residential real property
Summary: Relates to the removal of unauthorized persons from residential real property by a police officer if such unauthorized person(s) has been asked to leave and is not a current or former tenant.
LawSection: Real Property Actions and Proceedings Law
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the real property actions and proceedings law, in relation to the removal of unauthorized persons from residential real property
